{"tid":2209303,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"葉玉卿大女胡芷欣三點式曬Fit爆身形　網民大讚同媽媽一樣性感","createTime":"2020-09-19T14:14:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T17:39:56.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"335faf0cf0fbb1ab0e83e9000dca92dc1dfd2c41","tid":2209303,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T14:14:21.000Z","msg":"性感女神葉玉卿的美國華人富商老公胡兆明早前申請破產重組，幸好情況不是很嚴重，其大女胡芷欣（Victoria）不時在社交平台更新近況，日常生活未有受到太大影響。Victoria遺傳了媽媽的驕人身材和美貌，她今日（19/9）在IG上載了於室內穿三點式泳衣的照片，大曬Fit爆身形兼散發成熟女人味。Victoria留言寫着：「Pretending it&rsquo;s summer while I still can（仍然可以假扮是夏天）」。網民大讚Victoria同媽媽一樣性感：「身材火辣」、「卿姐的樣子」。"},{"pid":"ec2e2d44ee51364774a3bd1816b59f9436f96ab0","tid":2209303,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T14:14:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200919/384037721355718656.jpeg/A8l0ccKFYIUIkfHjg6uPzNaCSelF-oqk9020r_dNtK8?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200919%2F384037721355718656.jpeg%2FA8l0ccKFYIUIkfHjg6uPzNaCSelF-oqk9020r_dNtK8%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=22d46ecd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4495562/org/ca5a07c20a65d4520e3ac7fd41a4ac3d.png/UUuyFMjN6Ca9LUDDFYdAAJ-dmicyxnwF2dhrE9nYaxM?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4495562%2Forg%2Fca5a07c20a65d4520e3ac7fd41a4ac3d.png%2FUUuyFMjN6Ca9LUDDFYdAAJ-dmicyxnwF2dhrE9nYaxM%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=6b94d5e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4309080/org/b1242314aa524c34f7fbf6dfce2c3410.jpg/nXmVVnOPw-h82Hh0cqqoMJJGmABJeGgT_J6rgfyeq4E?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4309080%2Forg%2Fb1242314aa524c34f7fbf6dfce2c3410.jpg%2FnXmVVnOPw-h82Hh0cqqoMJJGmABJeGgT_J6rgfyeq4E%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=8b5763e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c208af4bb51a3d8ebb1bccea3d7107e07